text: "Myself" is a single by Canadian rapper Nav. It was released on January 12, 2016, as the second single from his self-titled debut mixtape and was produced and written by him himself. The song has since peaked at number five on the Billboard Bubbling Under R&B;/Hip-Hop Singles chart. ==Music video== The music video for "Myself" was released on March 22, 2017, directed by Nicholas Ruff, Cailin Lowry and Carver Karaszewski from Nuclear Creative.
